name: Dark Theme for Facebook
description:
I made this for personal use few months ago. I think it pretty nice so now i decide to share it, hope you guys like it.
I can't or just not yet access to all facebook pages to re-color them, so there will be some pages that not colored right.
additional_info:
- Added new found elements.
- Removed unnecessary classes.

This might be the last update, Facebook has released a new design that comes with dark mode.
